                "imgDesc": "You will sometimes find special bookshelves used to store grimoires within the castle.<br>Place the grimoires you find within the castle back onto the shelves to activate the musical power within.",
                "key": "Page 1/2"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character69118",
