                "imgDesc": "<p>Use the power of the \"symphony\" to resonate with activated bookshelves. <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Hold to unleash a Play Soundwave</span> that will cause the grimoires to fly off the shelves, and<span style=\"color: #FFE14B\"> Press to unleash a Pause Soundwave</span> that will stop them in mid-air.<br>If you can stop the grimoires in just the right positions, perhaps you can open the routes hidden behind the bookshelves...</p>",
